OL,3,C'We must be better than this': Swann's
OL,4,CCovid plea to ministers
OL,6,FRobin Swann urged an end to the
OL,7,F"nonsense" of ministerial colleagues
OL,8,Fmaking public attacks on Executive
OL,9,Fdecisions over lockdown restrictions
OL,10,Fduring a rise in Covid cases in 2020.
OL,12,FThe letter from Northern Ireland's
OL,13,FHealth Minister to then-first and
OL,14,Fdeputy first ministers Arlene Foster
OL,15,Fand Michelle O'Neill is among
OL,16,Fdocuments released on the Covid
OL,17,Finquiry website.
