OL,3,C'We must be better than this': Swann's
OL,4,CCovid plea to ministers
OL,6,FMr Swann told Ms Foster and Ms O'Neill
OL,7,Fof his "significant frustration and
OL,8,Fconcern", adding, the "simple truth is
OL,9,Fwe must be better than this".
OL,11,FThe letter was sent on October 17
OL,12,F2020, at a time when infections were
OL,13,Fon the rise as the second Covid wave
OL,14,Fhit Northern Ireland.
OL,16,FThe day before, then-agriculture
OL,17,Fminister Edwin Poots had claimed in a
OL,18,Fmedia interview that the incidence of
OL,19,Fthe virus was higher in nationalist
OL,20,Fareas than it was in unionist ones.
