OL,3,C'We must be better than this': Swann's
OL,4,CCovid plea to ministers
OL,6,FHe later denied linking the spread of
OL,7,FCovid-19 to religion, accusing rivals
OL,8,Fof "twisting and distorting" his
OL,9,Fcomments.
OL,11,FHe also expressed "grave reservations"
OL,12,Fabout new Covid-19 restrictions
OL,13,Fimposed by the Executive, of which he
OL,14,Fwas a member.
OL,16,FMr Swann did not mention Mr Poots in
OL,17,Fhis letter but stated his "deep
OL,18,Fconcern" about media comments.
