OL,3,C'We must be better than this': Swann's
OL,4,CCovid plea to ministers
OL,6,FHe said: "As you are aware, one of the
OL,7,Fkey challenges we face in battling the
OL,8,FCovid-19 pandemic is the lack of
OL,9,Fcompliance across the community, much
OL,10,Fof which has been attributed to
OL,11,Fconfusion as regards the position in
OL,12,Frespect of both restrictions and
OL,13,Fguidance.
OL,15,F"In this context it is clear that this
OL,16,Fis a time for everyone in positions of
OL,17,Fresponsibility to unite behind public
OL,18,Fhealth messages and agreed public
OL,19,Fhealth measures.
