OL,3,C'We must be better than this': Swann's
OL,4,CCovid plea to ministers
OL,6,F"It is particularly disturbing,
OL,7,Ftherefore, that a Ministerial
OL,8,Fcolleague has taken to the airwaves to
OL,9,Fadd further to that confused position.
OL,11,F"This can only be damaging to our
OL,12,Ffight against this virus, and may
OL,13,Fserve to undermine our position, with
OL,14,Fpotentially very damaging consequences
OL,15,Ffor members of the community we serve."
OL,17,FMr Swann's letter said there had been
OL,18,FExecutive agreement on the way forward.
