OL,3,C'We must be better than this': Swann's
OL,4,CCovid plea to ministers
OL,6,FHe also recorded his "deep concern" at
OL,7,Fpublic criticism of chief medical
OL,8,Fofficer Sir Michael McBride and chief
OL,9,Fscientific adviser Professor Ian Young.
OL,11,FHis letter said: "I am clearly of the
OL,12,Fview that it is simply not acceptable
OL,13,Ffor individual Ministers to give
OL,14,Fmisleading or fictional accounts of
OL,15,Fconfidential conversations and advice
OL,16,Ffrom officials."
OL,18,FMr Swann added: "All of this, of
OL,19,Fcourse, is easily avoidable by a
OL,20,Fgreater display of collective
OL,21,Fresponsibility by all Ministers.
