OL,3,C'We must be better than this': Swann's
OL,4,CCovid plea to ministers
OL,6,F"The simple reality is that is not a
OL,7,Fgame, and it is not overstating
OL,8,Fmatters to say it is a battle of life
OL,9,Fand death.
OL,11,F"We must act maturely and deal with
OL,12,Fthe complex issues before us and then
OL,13,Fseek to openly engage the public with
OL,14,Fa singular and clear message about
OL,15,Fhow, as a society, we can battle this
OL,16,Fdreadful virus.
