OL,3,C'We must be better than this': Swann's
OL,4,CCovid plea to ministers
OL,6,F"I have chosen not to make a detailed
OL,7,Fpublic statement as regards my
OL,8,Fsignificant frustration and concern
OL,9,Fwith these events, and hope that
OL,10,Fairing them through this route can
OL,11,Fbetter achieve an end to such nonsense.
OL,13,F"The simple truth is we must be better
OL,14,Fthan this."
